Vertical Petroleum Industries LLC $794,000 Financing
Vertical Petroleum Industries LLC just submitted form D announcing $794,000 financing.  This is a new filing. Vertical Petroleum Industries LLC was able to sell $79,400. That is 10% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $794,000. The financing was made by 1 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $10,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-10-25. Vertical Petroleum Industries LLC is based in  10 W MAIN ST, SUITE 603  ARDMORE 73401. The firm's business is Oil and Gas. The firm's revenue range is $1 - $1,000,000. The form was signed by  Daniel Sauer.





